title: Can't See Own Club!
body:
Ever since I upgraded to the new client, I have not been able to see my own club.
I am the original creator and current owner, and when I ask my friends, they say it says I am in the club.
I  submitted a support ticket, but received no response. Help me pls.
The club is named Kukki Monster and the tag is Quota.

replies.body: Your club might have been out of sync.  I've processed a refresh so hopefully it should be okay now!  Also, sorry for the delay in ticket response our volume might be a bit higher than usual.  You may need to relog before seeing the club!
Thank you so much, I literally love you now!
